#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is switched on, selecting an item from the history causes &klipper; "
"to display the actions pop-up on that item, if appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Kui see on lubatud, sunnib elemendi valimine ajaloost &klipper;i hüpikmenüüs "
"näitama selle puhul võimalikke tegevusi (kui neid on)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove white space when executing actions"
msgstr "Toimingute rakendamisel eemaldatakse tühimärk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If selected, any white space (spaces, tabs, &etc;) at the beginning and end "
"of the clipboard contents will be removed before passing the clipboard "
"contents to an application. This is useful, for example, if the clipboard "
"contains a &URL; with spaces which, if opened by a web browser, would cause "
"an error."
msgstr ""
"Mõnikord on valitud tekstil lõpus tühimärke, mis &URL;-ina lehitsejas "
"avatuna võivad tekitada vigu. Selle võimaluse sisselülitamine eemaldab "
"valitud stringi lõpust ja algusest kõik tühimärgid (lõikepuhvri algupärast "
"sisu ei muudeta)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:303
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Enable MIME-based actions"
msgid "Include MIME actions"
msgstr "MIME-põhiste toimingute lubamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If selected, in addition to the actions you defined a list of "
#| "applications for the detected MIME type will appear in the popup menu."
msgid ""
"If selected, include applications that can accept its &MIME; type of a file "
"name or URL selected in the popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Valimise korral ilmub hüpikmenüüs lisaks määratud toimingutele nähtavale "
"veel rakenduste loend vastavalt tuvastatud MIME tüübile."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:312
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Actions Options"
msgid "Actions Configuration"
msgstr "Tegevuste valikud"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Expressions/Actions"
msgstr "Regulaaravaldise/tegevuse redigeerimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the <guilabel>Actions</guilabel> page, double-click the regular "
"expression or action that you want to edit or select it and press the "
"<guibutton>Edit Action</guibutton> button. A dialog will appear in which the "
"expression text can be edited as you wish."
msgstr ""
"Tee kaardil <guilabel>Tegevused</guilabel> topeltklõps regulaaravaldisel või "
"tegevusel, mida soovid redigeerida, või vali see ja klõpsa nupule "
"<guibutton>Muuda tegevust</guibutton>. Ilmub dialoog, kus saad avaldise "
"teksti oma tahtmist mööda muuta."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Expressions/Actions"
msgstr "Regulaaravaldise/tegevuse lisamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click the <guibutton>Add Action...</guibutton> button to add a regular "
#| "expression for &klipper; to match. &klipper; uses &Qt;'s "
#| "<classname>QRegExp</classname>, which understands most regular "
#| "expressions as you would use in <application>grep</application> or "
#| "<application>egrep</application> for instance."
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Add Action...</guibutton> button to add a regular "
"expression for &klipper; to match. &klipper; uses &Qt;'s "
"<classname>QRegularExpression</classname>, which uses PCRE (Perl Compatible "
"Regular Expressions)."
msgstr ""
"Kui soovid lisada regulaaravaldise, mida &klipper; saaks kasutada, klõpsa "
"nupule <guibutton>Lisa tegevus...</guibutton> &klipper; kasutab &Qt; klassi "
"<classname>QRegExp</classname>, mis tunnistab enamikku regulaaravaldisi, "
"mida kasutatakse näiteks rakendustes <application>grep</application> või "
"<application>egrep</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a description of the regular expression type (&eg; <quote>HTTP "
"URL</quote>) by <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking in the "
"<guilabel>Description</guilabel> column."
msgstr ""
"Regulaaravaldise kirjelduse (&eg; <quote>HTTP URL</quote>) saab lisada hiire "
"<mousebutton>vasaku</mousebutton> nupu klõpsuga veerul <guilabel>Kirjeldus</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can find detailed information about the use of <classname>QRegExp</"
#| "classname> regular expressions at <ulink url=\"http://doc.qt.io/qt-5/"
#| "qregexp.html#details\">http://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregexp.html#details</"
#| "ulink>. Note that &klipper; does not support the wildcard mode mentioned "
#| "on this page."
msgid ""
"You can find detailed information about the use of "
"<classname>QRegularExpression</classname> regular expressions in <ulink url="
"\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html#details\">the Qt upstream "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Põhjaliku info <classname>QRegExp</classname> regulaaravaldiste kasutamise "
"kohta leiab internetis aadresil <ulink url=\"http://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregexp."
"html#details\">http://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregexp.html#details</ulink>. Pane "
"tähele, et &klipper; ei toeta seal mainitud metamärkide kasutamist."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit the regular expression as described above. To add a command to execute, "
"click <guimenuitem>Add Command</guimenuitem> and edit the command in an in-"
"place text editing box. Double-clicking on a command allows you to edit it."
msgstr ""
"Redigeeri regulaaravaldist sarnaselt eespool kirjeldatule. Käivitatava käsu "
"lisamiseks klõpsa <guimenuitem>Lisa käsk</guimenuitem> ning redigeeri käsku "
"aktiveeruvas tekstikastis. Topeltklõps käsul võimaldab seda muuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that <token>%s</token> in the command line is replaced with the "
"clipboard contents, &eg; if your command definition is "
"<userinput><command>kwrite</command> <token>%s</token></userinput> and your "
"clipboard contents are <filename>/home/phil/textfile</filename>, the command "
"<userinput><command>kwrite</command> <filename>/home/phil/textfile</"
"filename></userinput> will be run. To include <token>%s</token> in the "
"command line, escape it with a backslash, as so: <userinput>\\%s</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Pane tähele, et parameeter <token>%s</token> asendatakse käsureal "
"lõikepuhvri sisuga, &eg; kui käsk on <userinput><command>kwrite</command> "
"<token>%s</token></userinput> ja lõikepuhvri sisu <filename>/home/pets/"
"tekstifail</filename>, siis käivitatakse käsk <userinput><command>kwrite</"
"command><filename>/home/pets/tekstifail</filename></userinput>. Et käsurida "
"parameetrit <token>%s</token> arvestaks, tuleb see märkida längkriipsuga: "
"<userinput>\\%s</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries <userinput><token>%0</token></userinput> through <userinput><token>"
"%9</token></userinput> will be replaced by the corresponding captured texts "
"from the match pattern."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts Options"
msgstr "Kiirklahvide valikud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The shortcuts page allows you to change the keyboard shortcuts which are "
"used to access &klipper; functions. You can change the shortcut to one of "
"three things:"
msgstr ""
"Kiirklahvide kaart võimaldab muuta klahvikombinatsioone, mida saab kasutada "
"&klipper;i võimaluste rakendamiseks. Väärtusi saab muuta järgmiselt:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid "None"
msgstr "Puudub"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selected action cannot be accessed directly from the keyboard"
msgstr ""
"Valitud tegevust ei saa esile kutsuda klaviatuurilt antava otsekorraldusega"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Vaikeväärtus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selected action uses &klipper;'s default key. These are the shortcuts "
"referred to in this manual."
msgstr ""
"Valitud tegevuseks kasutatakse &klipper;i vaikimisi määratud kiirklahvi. "
"Need on samad, millest on juttu käesolevas käsiraamatus."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Kohandatud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "The selected action is assigned to the keys you choose."
msgstr "Valitud tegevust rakendatakse sinu määratud klahvidega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose a custom key for the action you have selected, click on "
"<guilabel>Custom</guilabel> and then <guilabel>None</guilabel>. Now type the "
"desired key combination on your keyboard, as in any &kde; application."
msgstr ""
"Kohandatud klahvi määramiseks klõpsa <guilabel>Kohandatud</guilabel> ja siis "
"<guilabel>Puudub</guilabel>. Nüüd sisesta soovitud kombinatsioon täpselt "
"samamoodi, nagu see käib muudes &kde; rakendustes."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you define a shortcut for <guilabel>Open Klipper at Mouse Position</"
"guilabel> pressing this shortcut will open the &klipper; popup menu at the "
"position of the mouse cursor, instead of their default position (in the "
"&plasma; Panel). Useful if you use the mouse more than the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Kui määrad kiirklahvi käsule <guilabel>Klipper avatakse hiirekursori "
"asukohas</guilabel>, paneb selle kiirklahvi kasutamine &klipper;i hüpikmenüü "
"ilmuma seal, kus asub hiirekursor, selle asemel, et seda tavapäraselt "
"&plasma; paneelil avada. See võib olla kasulik, kui oled harjunud hiirt "
"klaviatuurist enam kasutama."

