#~ "option is selected, the selection and the clipboard is kept the same, so "
#~ "that anything in the selection is immediately available for pasting "
#~ "elsewhere using any method, including the traditional middle mouse "
#~ "button. Otherwise, the selection is recorded in the clipboard history, "
#~ "but the selection can only be pasted using the middle mouse button. Also "
#~ "see the <guilabel>Ignore selection</guilabel> option. See <xref linkend="
#~ "\"clipboard-modes\"/>."
